I took 1st Booster dose (Covishield) today. I went there in short notice and hence, facing some system issue. Excellent cooperation by the hospital team to resolve my issue. Moreover, they are very transparent and address any query you may have on Vaccine. Very expert staff who are administering Vaccine. Special thanks to Dr. Asha.

Dr.Sachin Borawake Sir has been our family physician for more than last 6-7 years. He is highly experienced and well qualified doctor around here. Hospital have almost all the facilities from Laboratory to X-Ray and even COVID vaccination is available here. Best part  about him is that ,his focus is not just on curative measures but preventive measures as well which is very unique. ( Eg like sometimes giving vitamin supplements along with normal curative medicines)
Overall very nice experience till date.
